  <entry>
    <title>远程桌面</title>
    <link href="https://adeuxy.com/post/yuan-cheng-zhuo-mian/"/>
    <id>https://adeuxy.com/post/yuan-cheng-zhuo-mian/</id>
    <published>2018-12-23T06:04:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-02-24T09:05:00.877Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>需要远程控制Windows，迫于teamviewer开始收费，识别为商业账号，连接5分钟就断开。换！</p><h2 id="frp"><a href="#frp" class="headerlink" title="frp"></a>frp</h2><p>很好用，用于内网穿透<br>服务端：<br>基本不用修改配置，直接启动就可以了</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">frps.ini</span><br><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line">bind_port = 7000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nohup ./frps -c frps.ini &gt; frps.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>客户端：<br>需要修改为服务端的ip地址，其他配置自己随便</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">frpc.ini</span><br><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line">server_addr = 服务端的ip地址</span><br><span class="line">server_port = 7000</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[RDP]</span><br><span class="line">type = tcp</span><br><span class="line">local_ip = 127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">local_port = 3389</span><br><span class="line">remote_port = 6000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动客户端</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">frpc -c frpc.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现Win 10 家庭版的 没有远程桌面设置，无语微软。。。</p><h2 id="RDPWrap"><a href="#RDPWrap" class="headerlink" title="RDPWrap"></a>RDPWrap</h2><p>使用RDPWrap<br>以管理员身份执行install.bat就安装完了。<br>之后打开RDPConf.exe查看是否正常，如果没有listening，那么需要替换rdpwrap.ini文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\Program Files\RDP Wrapper\rdpwrap.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>替换后去服务里重启remote desktop service就正常了。<br>最终：<br>通过服务端IP地址:6000就可以远程桌面到内网的Windows机器啦~</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
